setting up sentry

SENTRY is a powerful error tracking and monitoring tool that helps developers identify and fix issues in their applications. It provides real-time insights into errors, performance issues, and user interactions, allowing developers to quickly address problems and improve the overall user experience.

it would send you an email whenever an error occurs in your application, along with detailed information about the error, such as the stack trace, user context, and environment details. This allows you to quickly identify and fix issues before they impact a large number of users.
